<?xml version="1.0"?>
<!DOCTYPE rpl PUBLIC "-//ROCKLYTE//DTD RPL 1.0//EN">

<info>
 <title>Logic Tests</title>
 <author>Paul Manias</author>
 <keywords>logic, test</keywords>
 <description>Runs basic logic tests against the parser.</description>
</info>

<body font-size="10pt"/>

<page name="Index">

<h1>If Statement Tests</h1>

<p>There should be five successful tests following this paragraph.</p>

<if test="1 lt 2">
  <p>1. If statement satisfied.</p>
</if>
<else>
  <p>1. If statement failed.</p>
</else>

<if test="1 gt 2">
  <p>2. If statement failed.</p>
</if>
<else>
  <p>2. Else condition satisfied.</p>
</else>

<if test="1 gt 2">
  <p>3. If statement failed.</p>
</if>
<elseif test="1 lt 2">
  <p>3. Else-If statement satisfied.</p>
</elseif>
<else>
  <p>3. If statement failed.</p>
</else>

<if test="'true' != ''">
  <p>4. If-NotNull satisfied.</p>
</if>

<if test="empty(())">
  <p>5. If-Null conditional satisfied.</p>
</if>

<h2>Repeat Tests</h2>

<p>This repeating section will print numbers from 0 to 9.</p>

<p indent="40"><repeat start="0" end="10"><print value="{$loop?index}"/> </repeat></p>

<p>This while loop will print numbers from 0 to 4.</p>

<p indent="40"><while test="$loop?index lt 5"><print value="{$loop?index}"/> </while></p>

<h2>Special Variable Tests</h2>

<font face="courier">
<p>Current font: <print value="Style {$style?font-style}; Face {$style?font-face}; Size {$style?font-size}; Fill {$style?font-fill}"/></p>
<!-- Runtime-specific values such as timestamps, random numbers, paths, and platform names are intentionally excluded
from the hash-checked suite because they would vary between runs. -->
<p>Line Number: <print value="{$meta?line-no}"/></p>
<p>Page Name: <print value="{$meta?current-page}"/></p>
<p>Viewport size: <print value="{$layout?view-width} x {$layout?view-height}"/></p>
</font>

<h2>Escape Codes</h2>

<p>The line below tests use of the '{{' and '}}' characters to prevent translation of attribute values.  The string should be printed complete with untranslated object, argument and bracket references.</p>

<p indent><print value="{{$meta?author}}"/></p>

<p>Here is the same XQuery string, translated:</p>

<p indent><print value="{$meta?author}"/></p>

</page>
